{"tid":596044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Evgenia BB:「每次退賽，都令我十分難過。」","createTime":"2018-03-17T09:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T14:58:18.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a626e88a2fe9a212e62a865ffc4e62703bfbd4","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/168975?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=sports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F168975%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dsports&d=VYmZ4YKFRU2EKBODof7%2B0J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=15153887\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/168975?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=sports</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯雙姝梅德韋傑娃（Evgenia Medvedeva）及薩姬杜娃（Alina Zagitova）上月閃耀平昌冬奧，最後15歲師妹薩姬杜娃以1.31分之差，擊敗師姐梅德韋傑娃，贏得個人首面女子花式溜冰奧運金牌。在今月舉行的世界錦標賽，外界預計這對俄國師姐妹將再碰頭，但18歲的梅德韋傑娃宣布，其右腳傷勢復發，未能參加今年的世界賽，無法爭取3連冠。在梅德韋傑娃缺席之下，薩姬杜娃很大機會贏得今年的世界冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n兩屆世界賽及歐洲賽冠軍梅德韋傑娃對退賽感到十分失望，「每次退賽，都令我十分難過。這不是我首次錯過的比賽，但當比賽展開後，我要坐在沙發上看電視直播，我將會更加難過。因為健康原因，所以作出這個決定，醫生表示我需要時間康復。」<br />\n<br />\n梅德韋傑娃去年底受右腳傷患影響，缺席了去年12月的大獎賽總決賽，而薩姬杜娃在這個比賽贏得冠軍。雖然梅德韋傑娃之後復出戰歐洲賽及冬奧，但都不敵師妹薩姬杜娃。俄羅斯花式溜冰總會日前表示，梅德韋傑娃在冬奧一直忍痛比賽，而當她回國後，痛楚加劇；經過檢查後，醫生認為她要減輕腳部的負荷，估計她要養傷至少兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1282574/xlarge/793e81279682ad0bf2587089550ff8da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1282574%2Fxlarge%2F793e81279682ad0bf2587089550ff8da.jpg&h=8279b530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅德韋傑娃在冬奧忍痛作戰。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95298193f257b5a78f779bd887b1809b2671b5d","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071e4868a209b07de1fc5c2672a2bdbf970bef1c","tid":596044,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"5c929f9e4fdba74d1ee39f289c5ecef95a916602","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"071e4868a209b07de1fc5c2672a2bdbf970bef1c","tid":596044,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"G"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"又針對"},{"pid":"9f1fdc227b55804c947b910c037f9dacbbd6a217","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db5361a8cd24c6e696c402430c35126ebcd2a3b","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0100998665a127d7ad461ff40aaf000768a38c6","tid":596044,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/232444_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F232444_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=7ba62a07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc53a2bdf1b3cae9779cd631dc3e27d35f5be0e6","tid":596044,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0100998665a127d7ad461ff40aaf000768a38c6","tid":596044,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/232444_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ese